#: ../../language/error_codes/E3801.md:1
msgid "E3801"
msgstr "E3801"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E3801.md:3
msgid "Compiler diagnostic name: `inclusive_range_pattern_missing_equal`."
msgstr "编译器诊断名称：`inclusive_range_pattern_missing_equal`。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E3801.md:5
msgid "Range pattern is missing `=`."
msgstr "范围模式缺少 `=`。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E3801.md:7
msgid ""
"Range patterns must spell out whether the upper bound is inclusive or "
"exclusive. Use `a..=b` for an inclusive range and `a..<b` for an "
"exclusive range."
msgstr ""
"范围模式必须明确上界是包含还是排除。包含上界的范围请使用 `a..=b`，排除上界的"
"范围请使用 `a..<b`。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E3801.md:10
msgid "Erroneous example"
msgstr "错误示例"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E3801.md:12
msgid ""
"fn classify(x : Int) -> Unit {\n"
"  match x {\n"
"    1..2 => ()\n"
"    _ => ()\n"
"  }\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E3801.md:16
msgid ""
"`1..2` is not accepted as a pattern because it does not say whether `2` "
"is included."
msgstr "`1..2` 不能作为模式使用，因为它没有说明是否包含 `2`。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E3801.md:19
msgid "Suggestion"
msgstr "建议"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E3801.md:21
msgid "Choose an inclusive or exclusive range pattern explicitly."
msgstr "显式选择包含上界或排除上界的范围模式。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E3801.md:23
msgid ""
"fn classify(x : Int) -> Unit {\n"
"  match x {\n"
"    1..=2 => ()\n"
"    _ => ()\n"
"  }\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

